The Lonely Path~
The small pathway leads you deeper into the forest. It is fairly peaceful
here, although it does seem a bit gloomy. Soft light filters in through
the treetops, creating small, lonely patches of light upon the ground. You
don't know why, but you suddenly feel very lonely and sad.
  A warm black field has closed in behind you blocking your path back to
where you came. You notice a niche in the field however that could be a
some sort of keyhole.
  You can see something inscribed onto one of the trees.
~
