tree inscription~
Someone has enscribed something onto one of the trees. It reads:
 
        The hearts of the lonely and the tears of the sad
        These are the things that make this land.
        The Forest of Saddness is either friend or foe
        and could mean either the begining or the end.
        Fear not what lies here, lest you fear the pain in your heart;
        If you thought you knew hurt, real pain is about to start.
